column5: Does anyone know if there is a decent GPS map available yet for the NE section of Lac Seul? Say from Bear Narrows North. Thanks

I have Navionics Platinum North which includes Lac Seul. No map is 100% accurate however the houseboat routes and the X marks that signify rock are pretty good. The depth contours are very basic but it's much better than nothing.
trakmaps and navionics are the only two that I'm aware of.
